<Layout title="About AOLar.no">
  <main class="grid min-h-[50vh] place-content-center p-2 max-w-lg mx-auto">
    <h1 class="font-semibold">About AOLar.no</h1>
    <p class="text-xl p-4">Aolar.no is a webspace for exploration, tinkering and testing new stuff. </p>
    <p class="text-md p-4">Anders Øksendal Larsen is me... a dude interested in bicycles, frontend-develpment, Lego and other things. Current occupation; bicycle mechanic, ski-technician and "him with the beard" for <a class="text-green-600 hover:text-green-800 focus:text-green-800 hover:underline dark:text-green-200 dark:hover:text-green-300 dark:focus:text-green-300 transition-all duration-300 ease-in-out" href="https://sport1.no/butikker/sport1royken/">Sport1 Røyken</a></p>
