      <h2 class="font-semibold">This site is:</h2>
      <p>- created with <a class="text-green-600 hover:text-green-800 focus:text-green-800 hover:underline dark:text-green-200 dark:hover:text-green-300 dark:focus:text-green-300 transition-all duration-300 ease-in-out" href="https://astro.build">Astro</a> &amp; <a class="text-green-600 hover:text-green-800 focus:text-green-800 hover:underline dark:text-green-200 dark:hover:text-green-300 dark:focus:text-green-300 transition-all duration-300 ease-in-out" href="https://tailwindcss.com/">Tailwindcss</a></p>
