        </p><a href="https://app.netlify.com/sites/aolar/deploys" class="flex"><img class="self-center" alt="netlify status badge" src="https://api.netlify.com/api/v1/badges/4ce45616-d7c6-4d16-bd5c-2eb5c9a5f300/deploy-status"></a>        
      </div>

    </section>
  </main>
</Layout>